jsonvalues

Interface JsNumber

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JsElem
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsBigDec, JsBigInt, JsDouble, JsInt, JsLong

    public interface JsNumber
extends JsElem
    Represents an immutable json number. It's a marker interface for the types JsInt, JsLong, JsDouble, JsBigInt and JsBigDec
